# Bazel-compatible toolchain configuration
# In Bazel mode, C/C++ toolchains are auto-detected via rules_cc's
# cc_configure module extension. No manual toolchain setup needed here.

# This file intentionally left mostly empty - the cc_configure extension
# in rules_cc automatically creates @local_config_cc with the detected
# C/C++ toolchain, which is registered via register_toolchains() in
# MODULE.bazel or the extension itself.
